title: Archer finishes with five wickets as Australia bowled out for 371
subtitle: Jofra Archer removes Mitchell Starc and Nathan Lyon on the morning of day two to finish with figures of 5-53,  earning his fourth career Test five-wicket haul as England bowl Australia out for 371 in their first innings of the third Ashes Test in Adelaide.
full_text: Jofra Archer removes Mitchell Starc and Nathan Lyon on the morning of day two to finish with figures of 5-53,  earning his fourth career Test five-wicket haul as England bowl Australia out for 371 in their first innings of the third Ashes Test in Adelaide.
